        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "For privacy reasons, and because the user’s location can change, the map item returned by this method does not contain any coordinate data. When you need the actual location of the user, you must use the Core Location framework to retrieve it."
